<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221217>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Manota appendiculata sp. n. (A paratype from French Guyana, B, C, D holotype). A. Antennal flagellomere 4, lateral view. B. Hypopygium, dorsal view. C. Hypopygium, ventral view. D. Aedeagus and hypoproct, ventral view. E. Gonostylus, dorsal view. F. Juxtagonostylar megasetae, dorsal view. Scale 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221217/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

